Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往天空 亲近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔于天空的神秘力量开始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天之边际云之彼方存在着一片黄金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事讲述了一个追寻梦想自由生存的天空盗贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空盗团少年——酷的波澜起伏的爱和冒险的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.68,0:02:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继蕾之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到达煌珠乐园的酷他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.41,0:02:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有着和人类社会一样的生活过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.99,0:02:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家各自奋战之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.65,0:02:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使在宝座之上的蕾加冕为女王的仪式开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷虽然逼近至咫尺之遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但受到出现在眼前的ChaosChoir的干部们的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其生命之线不费吹灰之力就被剪断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.65,0:02:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有谁能救蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.73,0:02:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此下去ChaosChoir得以统治人类了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.64,0:03:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十五唱 ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的同契者已经收拾掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来那孩子就完完全全属于我们的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.77,0:03:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举行蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人加冕为女王的仪式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.64,0:04:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在煌珠乐园的周围战斗好像还在继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.60,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人的话就要说到做到啊 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在磨磨蹭蹭地干什么 酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点结束这战争 酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.16,0:04:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能唤醒失去的颂词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去怎么办 希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出蕾 制止战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.91,0:05:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷也肯定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.31,0:06:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你加冕为煌珠乐园的女王的时刻终于到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭恭敬敬{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贺祝皇位继承{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊者无需开口{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.91,0:06:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉裳加身{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝颂七煌宝树{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风雅端庄{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有汝{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼等所依唯有公主{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻请登基{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承大统{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋万代歌颂{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢天喜地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚心诚意{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.46,0:06:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬奉上天{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.74,0:07:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭祀上苍之谬{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必得赎罪{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯洁之白{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神灵之弓{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏在心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此 一切准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.41,0:07:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让蕾做女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有什么目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能得到七煌宝树的强大力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击溃守护翼就易如反掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.81,0:07:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能把妨碍我们的人全部干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.37,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护翼已经决定停止攻击煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.43,0:08:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也请你们别再战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己打过来的就别随便命令别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是再这样打下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.40,0:08:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护者 拟煌珠 以及煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多很多的人都将受到伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.41,0:08:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把煌珠当作道具使其受伤的不是守护者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 我们是错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.91,0:08:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因为这样才不想争战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.82,0:08:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠和人类曾共同歌颂 创造奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也只要煌珠和人类同心协力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平共处是可以做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只追求战斗的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉创造奇迹的颂词的是守护者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有能唱颂那颂词的守护者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们携手是毫无必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠乐园的女王——蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人的强大力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之公主{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听吾之祷{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚这人心不古的世界{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.98,0:09:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.65,0:09:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是蕾的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.20,0:09:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没赶上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.48,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人的强大力量现在已是我们的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂回返{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.85,0:10:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身伏地上的男子{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥间之所{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只一墓地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有恋人{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待汝之归{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之生命{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献之于你{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,务请重返人世{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨此为愿{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.04,0:10:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.23,0:10:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.81,0:10:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.37,0:10:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为听到我的呼唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.19,0:11:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾才赶来煌珠乐园 被他们抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为心痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.59,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成为煌珠乐园的女王后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育了无数的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧珐斯他们所说的一切都照做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.93,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我已只剩下极其微薄的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.99,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去蕾会听任欧珐斯他们摆布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.29,0:12:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.87,0:12:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.11,0:12:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我力所能及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.08,0:12:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把生命给了我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.00,0:12:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段楼梯的尽头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蕾的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心爱之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.07,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么尽发生这么悲伤的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.94,0:13:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要终结这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你们的回答吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.48,0:13:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.15,0:14:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将要创造煌珠统治的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有这个是不想使用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙威 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把蕾封印起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是前辈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.05,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蕾的力量不能让ChaosChoir利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.32,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让其得逞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.12,0:14:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拜托你们掩护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.88,0:14:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.64,0:14:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.50,0:14:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你不是已经死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那么 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.90,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊芙她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的生命给了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.48,0:15:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确很像那个人的愚蠢做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直蛮横地利用伊芙的力量是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.82,0:15:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后当伊芙的力量耗尽了之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.42,0:15:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又妄想利用蕾的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.33,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事绝对不会让你们得逞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得到吗 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能听任这些家伙们的摆布
