Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.27,0:15:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.59,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人已成为煌珠乐园的女王了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的言语是听不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.53,0:15:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经死过一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.37,0:16:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬间 煌珠与同契者的关系消亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.64,0:16:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人之间已经没有任何牵连了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.98,0:16:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个把蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说“把蕾封印起来”吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外别无他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.61,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去蕾听任ChaosChoir摆布也不要紧吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你解开了封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你亲手...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.85,0:16:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.43,0:16:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
