Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以己之便或是利用或是封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事怎么做得到
