Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是煌珠乐园的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自说自话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是由蕾决定的
